	(14053, 'With all these feathers, I thought that Medivh was a druid.', NULL, 'Avec toutes ces plumes, je croyais que Medivh était un druide.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Con todas esas plumas, pensé que Medivh era una druida.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
